        "text_DycqGr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Founded nearly 30 years ago in Brunswick by Gabriel Katebian and Sam Abou-Khater, Cedar Hospitality began its journey as Cedar Catering & Refrigeration. Originally operating out of a corner shop, they found their feet selling tableware and other light catering equipment. Cousins Peter Campese and Danny Katebian took over the business from their father and uncle in 1995, taking to the road as they built their network all over Melbourne. From its humble beginnings on the corner of Michael Street and Sydney Road Brunswick, Cedar Hospitality now resides in one of Australia’s largest showrooms that spans 18,000 square metres.</p>",
            "subtext_color": true
          }
        }
