          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Welcome to our massive 95 square metre demonstration kitchen, thoughtfully designed to educate and guide you in making the right decisions when purchasing commercial equipment for your venue. We host live cooking<br/>demonstrations daily on coffee machines, fryers, combi ovens, speed ovens, benchtop equipment, dishwashers, refrigeration, ice machines, and much more. Our carefully crafted space allows large groups to engage, ask questions, and experience how a fully functioning kitchen operates—not just in front of house, but behind the scenes as well<br/><br/></p>",
