            "highlight_style": "none",
            "highlight_font_style": "italic",
            "highlight_style_color": "",
            "highlight_text_color": "",
            "heading_size": "h5",
            "text": "<p>High energy Japanese-inspired eating house. A celebration of food cooked over fire—meticulously conceived, inventively executed, riotously enjoyed. Set on the first floor of the landmark 80 Collins Street in the heart of Melbourne's fashion quarter, look up for the neon sign marking the entrance.</p>",
            "text_size": "text-sm",
            "button_label": "Read More",
            "button_link": "#",
            "button_style": "btn--underline",
            "button_icon": "none"
          }
        },
        "column_WRPAwc": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Instagram-Post-_-11_95b63afb-435a-46f4-87f1-d123d0846c96.png",
            "image_link": "",
            "subheading": "column",
            "title": "SET UP EXPERIENCE",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "highlight_font_style": "italic",
            "highlight_style_color": "",
            "highlight_text_color": "",
            "heading_size": "h5",
            "text": "<p>The 150-seat venue will host a main dining space, bar, and the eight-seat speakeasy La Rue which will also serve the main dining menu. The food offering has been curated by Executive chef Jacqui Challinor and Head Chef Brendan Katich and is inspired by classic French dishes.</p>",
            "text_size": "text-sm",
            "button_label": "Read More",
            "button_link": "#",
            "button_style": "btn--underline",
            "button_icon": "none"
          }
        },
        "column_ikYHeg": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Instagram-Post-_-39_7fcc6c62-06be-4bf9-a011-88aff33eb24e.png",
            "image_link": "",
            "subheading": "column",
            "title": "CUSTOM MADE PROCESS",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "highlight_font_style": "italic",
            "highlight_style_color": "",
            "highlight_text_color": "",
            "heading_size": "h5",
            "text": "<p>Our uncompromising approach to Quality, Design, Innovation, Customer Service and an unparalleled knowledge of the Commercial Food Service industry.</p>",
            "text_size": "text-sm",
            "button_label": "Read More",
            "button_link": "#",
            "button_style": "btn--underline",
            "button_icon": "none"
          }
        },
        "column_bTbVtm": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Cedar_OCT2022-135_2x_a0f28fc6-54a1-4bce-8e83-fa4458e38df8.png",
            "image_link": "",
            "subheading": "column",
            "title": "Visit our showroom.",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "highlight_font_style": "italic",
            "highlight_style_color": "",
            "highlight_text_color": "",
            "heading_size": "h5",
            "text": "<p>Led by Culinary Consultant Mark Ebbels, the menu draws on Helen and Joey’s Chinese Australian heritage, pairing refined Asian influenced flavours with premium local produce and estate grown wines. \u000b A focus on seasonal ingredients and wood fired cooking creates dishes that are expressive, balanced and deeply connected to place.</p>",
